{"tid":1776149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉載】國外插畫家將計就計利用爬蟲惡搞盜圖成衣網站","createTime":"2019-12-09T10:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T14:28:33.000Z","uid":82829,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f252ebcdefa530e80a746cbb1c8e29ec320f4d78","tid":1776149,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"[閒聊] 國外插畫家將計就計利用爬蟲惡搞盜圖成衣網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://hornydragon.blogspot.com/2019/12/shirts.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhornydragon.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F12%2Fshirts.html%3Fm%3D1&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FzrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=0c345104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hornydragon.blogspot.com/2019/12/shirts.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n消息來源：<a href=\"https://www.plurk.com/p/nlkfsq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plurk.com%2Fp%2Fnlkfsq&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FzrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=c080a090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.plurk.com/p/nlkfsq</a><br />\n<br />\n原twitter討論串：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Hannahdouken/status/1201853553050038273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHannahdouken%2Fstatus%2F1201853553050038273&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FzrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=9f79979e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHannahdouken%2Fstatus%2F1201853553050038273&h=e2c87a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Hannahdouken/status/1201853553050038273</a><br />\n<br />\n臺灣很多繪師應該都遇過自己的作品被別人隨意印成商品販售這檔事。<br />\n而且這些業者很多在海外，即使想抗議或檢舉也求助無門，<br />\n只得運用輿論壓力希望對方能自行下架，充滿了無力感。<br />\n最近有位國外的繪師懷疑某些成衣網站能如此迅速且大量地盜圖，<br />\n是藉由網路爬蟲程式的幫助，只要搜尋到諸如「這要是印成衣服我一定買」之類的字眼<br />\n就自動將圖片抓下來並直接在頁面上做成廣告展示。<br />\n為了驗證這個假設，他決定發起一個實驗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xpuHiudat8c/Xe4HG_QMJDI/AAAAAAAA4s4/I6E8j6yxWwYj4pPtvZs21w49l9_gxc0DgCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-xpuHiudat8c%2FXe4HG_QMJDI%2FAAAAAAAA4s4%2FI6E8j6yxWwYj4pPtvZs21w49l9_gxc0DgCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F01.jpg&h=1a2ddfcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-__jH3ngZoBk/Xe4HG93SuUI/AAAAAAAA4s8/st6kt8GN_aUNYaqdHtcBLn-5yHC71CFJgCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-__jH3ngZoBk%2FXe4HG93SuUI%2FAAAAAAAA4s8%2Fst6kt8GN_aUNYaqdHtcBLn-5yHC71CFJgCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F02.jpg&h=c865ad24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此時大家都只是抱著玩玩的實驗心態，紛紛在底下留言，<br />\n「我需要這件衣服！」「我希望看到這張圖被做成衣服！」等等，<br />\n誰都沒想到不到48個小時，這個假說就獲得了證實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BLdn1uvt3CQ/Xe4HHOWzWPI/AAAAAAAA4tA/GwBVX1PNhXMNZ--rKDcjmOLqfRcBi2hrwCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-BLdn1uvt3CQ%2FXe4HHOWzWPI%2FAAAAAAAA4tA%2FGwBVX1PNhXMNZ--rKDcjmOLqfRcBi2hrwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F03.jpg&h=56f3c461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n很明顯地，這些網站的確是用機器人自動抓圖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-adFqExpsDF8/Xe4HHbYRZ4I/AAAAAAAA4tE/vfnCJqzZoiQwfs1ETDA3v0zKjeZs_gtyACLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-adFqExpsDF8%2FXe4HHbYRZ4I%2FAAAAAAAA4tE%2FvfnCJqzZoiQwfs1ETDA3v0zKjeZs_gtyACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F04.jpg&h=f7b935ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n才一下子的功夫，<br />\n這張圖便攻佔了不只一間網路成衣廠商的版面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zDr_-FeQgKo/Xe4HH7uYEJI/AAAAAAAA4tQ/q2LWo38X0-8LZD05_lEHBPSQC2bqaET1ACLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-zDr_-FeQgKo%2FXe4HH7uYEJI%2FAAAAAAAA4tQ%2Fq2LWo38X0-8LZD05_lEHBPSQC2bqaET1ACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F06.jpg&h=f1189147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然鬧到不行，<br />\n但是這些機器人是怎麼把Stolen Art Shirt判定為衣服名稱的？？？<br />\n這些爬蟲程式似乎有點厲害......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但是不久之後，有些人認為這種舉動頂多只是在抗議，<br />\n根本無法實質影響這些網站，<br />\n於是有人想出了一個辦法......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fU9n_yGx5Cc/Xe4HHw1HZWI/AAAAAAAA4tM/3l5e00mLdhEWl1CEBnvW5i-_ThVY2HLKACLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-fU9n_yGx5Cc%2FXe4HHw1HZWI%2FAAAAAAAA4tM%2F3l5e00mLdhEWl1CEBnvW5i-_ThVY2HLKACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F07.jpg&h=dcef8767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讓網路爬蟲抓到那些<br />\n對版權最斤斤計較的超級大廠圖片！<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-LGgj84emzgs/Xe4HIeux7XI/AAAAAAAA4tY/TvYFoOQgn3MlfncGQNnQjv3eNyBJDxQlQCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LGgj84emzgs%2FXe4HIeux7XI%2FAAAAAAAA4tY%2FTvYFoOQgn3MlfncGQNnQjv3eNyBJDxQlQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F09.jpg&h=ac2fb210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8cHpeGzdDAo/Xe4HIsr0xAI/AAAAAAAA4tc/HyPXowOGADcLFe6H_D_cO-QRyUlBODBRACLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-8cHpeGzdDAo%2FXe4HIsr0xAI%2FAAAAAAAA4tc%2FHyPXowOGADcLFe6H_D_cO-QRyUlBODBRACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F10.jpg&h=3c31ca60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這.......這........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我腦中浮出的圖只有一張：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-u7G2Wf2jUwY/Xe4J0n3SBrI/AAAAAAAA4uE/JzPYc6XDZiUhEoDNHYBzoaCsalWU_vSpACLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/outstanding.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-u7G2Wf2jUwY%2FXe4J0n3SBrI%2FAAAAAAAA4uE%2FJzPYc6XDZiUhEoDNHYBzoaCsalWU_vSpACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2Foutstanding.jpg&h=701e2c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而網友們當然不會在這裡停下來，<br />\n他們懷疑這些網站的本部很有可能來自某個惡名昭彰的國家，<br />\n於是......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來這些圖片當然都被這些網站移除了，而這些網站依然好端端地存在著。<br />\n(編輯：可能是我瀏覽時的分區不同所以忽略了，絕大多數的圖片都還在，快笑死。)<br />\n難道這代表這次的實驗毫無價值嗎？不是的，經由這次實驗，<br />\n繪師們至少可以知道如何降低自己的作品被爬蟲抓走的機率：<br />\n在公開場合張貼自己的作品時，不要加入太多與商品相關的字眼，<br />\n要為了場次宣傳時商品時可以試著將資訊全部以圖片形式呈現，降低被偵測的機率，<br />\n同時呼籲讀者，看到想要商品化的東西時改用私訊聯絡，不要直接張貼於公開版面，<br />\n如此一來應能大大降低被第三方製成商品的可行性。<br />\n<br />\n可惡我真的很想看看中國廠商因為爬蟲把敏感資訊自動放到商品頁面上結果翻車的新聞......"},{"pid":"8c63d5d817592b24b7cd65cb161d444dd13326cf","tid":1776149,"uid":82829,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2G4QNyAgdUM/Xe4HIu6EDvI/AAAAAAAA4tg/NwmBsCOKm2A9wUNxby0vcTGHOw3EsaMaACLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-2G4QNyAgdUM%2FXe4HIu6EDvI%2FAAAAAAAA4tg%2FNwmBsCOKm2A9wUNxby0vcTGHOw3EsaMaACLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F11.jpg&h=66136301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「幫助香港！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你們以為這張的殺傷力的殺傷力已經夠大了嗎？<br />\n不，最經典的在下面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-r-wzLJHUJGI/Xe4KlhTNL8I/AAAAAAAA4uM/Tgy-EqkBbUY6H6LyNs00gfnqmjaxSv7KwCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-r-wzLJHUJGI%2FXe4KlhTNL8I%2FAAAAAAAA4uM%2FTgy-EqkBbUY6H6LyNs00gfnqmjaxSv7KwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F12.jpg&h=7e2ec4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這實在是太完美了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來這些圖片當然都被這些網站移除了，而這些網站依然好端端地存在著。<br />\n(編輯：可能是我瀏覽時的分區不同所以忽略了，絕大多數的圖片都還在，快笑死。)<br />\n難道這代表這次的實驗毫無價值嗎？不是的，經由這次實驗，<br />\n繪師們至少可以知道如何降低自己的作品被爬蟲抓走的機率：<br />\n在公開場合張貼自己的作品時，不要加入太多與商品相關的字眼，<br />\n要為了場次宣傳時商品時可以試著將資訊全部以圖片形式呈現，降低被偵測的機率，<br />\n同時呼籲讀者，看到想要商品化的東西時改用私訊聯絡，不要直接張貼於公開版面，<br />\n如此一來應能大大降低被第三方製成商品的可行性。<br />\n<br />\n可惡我真的很想看看中國廠商因為爬蟲把敏感資訊自動放到商品頁面上結果翻車的新聞......"},{"pid":"e9bc9df9af156c64be052893a29aa92adbac46d1","tid":1776149,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52b77c4304f2f132b620aa80cdc4ba41f898c02","tid":1776149,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"efdaf201e347db3ab2a2e7b395f06765df556187","tid":1776149,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc438efef65a17a50f034d823b332955a57311a","tid":1776149,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"超好笑"},{"pid":"238cdf1426d974c2f726fbb0083b5f4f8b7a32b2","tid":1776149,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"中國春袋是香港"},{"pid":"b5efef74905dd22cecb480f8b0aaec77d12216f0","tid":1776149,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"占占占.....人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f3984b38bbcb807eca00c1fe56773c64a2d7d0","tid":1776149,"uid":22409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"正呀喂"},{"pid":"56d49f2591ac873bc95c785550df7aaa628e9f9d","tid":1776149,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/